# Work hard, play hard!  Consider suffixing your commit messages with a relevant emoji for
# greater good:
#
#   :hammer: `:hammer:` when adding new class/fucntion
#   :construction_worker: `:construction_worker:` changes to update in requirement
#   :art: `:art:` when improving the format/structure of the code
#   :racehorse: `:racehorse:` when improving performance
#   :non-potable_water: `:non-potable_water:` when plugging memory leaks
#   :memo: `:memo:` when writing docs
#   :penguin: `:penguin:` when fixing something in Java file
#   :checkered_flag: `:checkered_flag:` when fixing something in layouts
#   :bug: `:bug:` when fixing a bug
#   :fire: `:fire:` when removing code or files
#   :green_heart: `:green_heart:` when fixing the CI build
#   :white_check_mark: `:white_check_mark:` when adding tests
#   :lock: `:lock:` when dealing with security
#   :arrow_up: `:arrow_up:` when upgrading dependencies
#   :arrow_down: `:arrow_down:` when downgrading dependencies
